ZH: 他瞒着家人给我买了一份礼物。
EN: He bought me a gift without telling his family.

ZH: 妈妈瞒着爸爸买了新衣服。
EN: Mom bought new clothes without telling dad.

ZH: 我瞒着朋友悄悄去了旅行。
EN: I went on a trip without telling my friends.

ZH: 他瞒着老板请了一天假。
EN: He took a day off without informing the boss.

ZH: 姐姐瞒着妹妹用她的化妆品。
EN: Big sister secretly used little sister's cosmetics without her knowing.

ZH: 我们瞒着他筹备了一个惊喜生日派对。
EN: We secretly planned a surprise birthday party without him knowing.

ZH: 他瞒着女朋友去了夜店。
EN: He went to the nightclub without telling his girlfriend.

ZH: 我瞒着家人买了一辆新车。
EN: I bought a new car without telling my family.

ZH: 她瞒着同事离开公司。
EN: She left the company without telling her colleagues.

ZH: 他瞒着妻子和朋友一起去打高尔夫球。
EN: He went golfing with friends without telling his wife.

ZH: 我们瞒着父母参加了音乐比赛。
EN: We participated in a music competition without telling our parents.

ZH: 她瞒着丈夫和朋友一起去旅行。
EN: She went on a trip with friends without telling her husband.

ZH: 我们瞒着老师放学后去游乐园。
EN: We went to the amusement park after school without telling the teacher.

ZH: 他瞒着儿子给他买了一本漫画书。
EN: He bought a comic book for his son without him knowing.

ZH: 她瞒着家人剪了个新发型。
EN: She got a new haircut without telling her family.

ZH: 我们瞒着领导讨论了一个新项目。
EN: We discussed a new project without informing our superiors.

ZH: 他瞒着房东养了一只宠物狗。
EN: He secretly kept a pet dog without telling the landlord.

ZH: 她瞒着男朋友参加了一个舞蹈课程。
EN: She attended a dance class without telling her boyfriend.

ZH: 我们瞒着同学去看了一场电影。
EN: We watched a movie without informing our classmates.

ZH: 她瞒着父母买了一本禁止出版的书。
EN: She bought a banned book without telling her parents.
